quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  47,30,"S־µ Y־µp־µ a nka Y־µde wֽ»n b־µkyer־µ mo ama mode wֽ»n nsohy־µde־µ ahu wֽ»n. Nokor־µ s־µ wode wֽ»n nne kasa bֹ›hu wֽ»n. Onyankopֽ»n nim mo dwumadie (nyinaa)."
  47,31,"Nokor־µ s־µ, Y־µb־µsֽ» mo ahw־µ kֽ»pem s־µ Y־µbֹ›hu mo mu mmֽ»demmֽ»foֽ» no ne aboter־µfoֽ» no, na Y־µb־µsֽ» mo ahw־µ wֽ» mons־µm mu."
  47,32,"Wֽ»n a wֽ»po nokorװ‘ na wֽ»si (amanfoֽ») kwan firi Nyankopֽ»n kwan no soֽ», na wֽ»ko tia ֶ†somafoֽ» no wֽ» akyire yi a ֽ»kwan tenenee no ada adi ama wֽ»n no, wֽ»ntumi nny־µ Nyankopֽ»n hwee na ֶ†b־µma wֽ»n nnwuma ay־µ kwa."
  47,33,"Mo a moagye adie, mony־µ sotie mma Nyankopֽ»n ne ne Somafoֽ» no, na monhw־µ na moans־µe mo nnwuma."
  47,34,"Nokor־µ s־µ, wֽ»n a wֽ»yi boniay־µ, na wֹ”si (amanfoֽ») kwan firi Nyankopֽ»n kwan no soֽ», na wֽ»wu wֽ» aber־µ a wֽ»y־µ (Kaafirifoֽ») boniay־µfoֽ» no, Onyankopֽ»n mfa wֽ»n bֽ»ne nky־µ wֽ»n."
  47,35,"Enti monhw־µ na moango mo ho any־µ s־µ de־µ morefr־µ wֽ»n akֽ» asomdwoeװ‘ (apam) mu; na mo ne nkonimdifoֽ», Onyankopֽ»n ka mo ho, na ֶ†mma mo nnwuma pa no so akatua so nte."
  47,36,"Wiase asetena yi y־µ agorֽ» ne ahurusie; na s־µ mogye di na mosuro Nyame a, ֶ†de moakatua b־µma mo, na ֶ†mmisa mo moagyapade־µ."
  47,37,"S־µ nka ֶ†rebisa mo (agyapade־µ no) ־µna ֶ†rehy־µ mo mpo a, nka mob־µy־µ ho p־µp־µ־µ; na ֶ†bֹ›yi moadwen bֽ»ne no adi."
  47,38,"Hw־µ, mone nkorֽ»foֽ» no a yֹ›afr־µ mo s־µ monyi (mosika) wֽ» Nyame kwan soֽ» no. Nanso mo mu bi wֽ» hֽ» a wֽ»y־µ p־µp־µ־µ (anaa wֽ»bֽ» ay־µmuֽ»nwono) na obi a ֽ»y־µ p־µp־µ־µ no, ֽ»y־µ p־µp־µ־µ no ma ne ho; na Nyankopֽ»n de־µ Wanya ne ho, mo na moy־µ ahiafoֽ»; na s־µ modane moakyi (ma Islam som no) a, ֶ†de amanfoֽ» foforֽ» b־µhy־µ mo anan mu, na wֽ»n de־µ wֽ»ny־µ tes־µ mo."